-42. DOI: 10.1158/0008-5472.CAN-14-2645<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Roy|first=Ishan|last2=McAllister|first2=Donna M.|last3=Gorse|first3=Egal|last4=Dixon|first4=Kate|last5=Piper|first5=Clinton T.|last6=Zimmerman|first6=Noah P.|last7=Getschman|first7=Anthony E.|last8=Tsai|first8=Susan|last9=Engle|first9=Dannielle D.|last10=Evans|first10=Douglas B.|last11=Volkman|first11=Brian F.|date=2015-09-01|title=Pancreatic Cancer Cell Migration and Metastasis Is Regulated by Chemokine-Biased Agonism and Bioenergetic Signaling|url=https://cancerres.aacrjournals.org/content/75/17/3529|journal=Cancer Research|language=en|volume=75|issue=17|pages=3529\u20133542|doi=10.1158/0008-5472.CAN-14-2645|issn=0008-5472}}</ref>\n* Boj, S.F.*, Hwang, C.I.*, Baker, L.A.*, Chio, I.I.*, Engle, D.D.*, Corbo, V.*, Jager, M.*, Ponz-Sarvise, M., Tiriac, H., Spector, M.S., Gracanin, A., Oni, T., Yu, K.H., van Boxtel, R., Huch, M., Rivera, K.D., Wilson, J.P., Feigin, M.E., \u00d6hlund, D., Handly-Santana, A., Ardito-Abraham, C.M., Ludwig, M., Elyada, E., Alagesan, B., Biffi, G., Yordanov, G.N., Delcuze, B., Creighton, B., Wright, K., Park, Y., Morsink, F.H., Molenaar, I.Q., Borel Rinkes, I.H., Cuppen, E., Hao, Y., Jin, Y., Nijman, I.J., Iacobuzio-Donahue, C., Leach, S.D., Pappin, D.J., Hammell, M., Klimstra, D.S., Basturk, O., Hruban, R.H., Offerhaus, G.J., Vries, R.G., Clevers, H., Tuveson, D.A. Organoid models of human and mouse ductal pancreatic cancer. (2015) ''Cell.'' 160(1-2):324-38. DOI: 10.1016/j.cell.2014.12.021<ref>{{Cite journal|last=Boj|first=Sylvia F.|last2=Hwang|first2=Chang-Il|last3=Baker|first3=Lindsey A.|last4=Chio|first4=Iok In Christine|last5=Engle|first5=Dannielle D.|last6=Corbo|first6=Vincenzo|last7=Jager|first7=Myrthe|last8=Ponz-Sarvise|first8=Mariano|last9=Tiriac|first9=Herv\u00e9|last10=Spector|first10=Mona S.|last11=Gracanin|first11=Ana|date=2015-01-15|title=Organoid models of human and mouse ductal pancreatic cancer|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/25557080|journal=Cell|volum